{"tid":93484,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人做賊真係有好多方法","createTime":"2017-01-24T12:49:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-24T12:49:53.000Z","uid":40190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"20b93efd169a1d968223f98dc32511b5430f9a72","tid":93484,"uid":40190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T12:49:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呃人都可以發達，仲做乜好人。<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/24/204939_ee0862b48c03c942fd124172b9b93278.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F24%2F204939_ee0862b48c03c942fd124172b9b93278.jpg&h=4e7bdbd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我們剛託京都市國際觀光大使致電去小山園查詢，得到下列回覆：「香港丸久小山園所販賣的已包裝商品，的確是跟小山園合作販賣的，但是關於咖啡店，即現場享用的蛋糕或點心等，是香港那邊自行開始販賣的，卻未有經過小山園同意。對於這件事情目前要怎麼處理，他們公司內部目前還在商討中。」<blockquote>引用</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/food/art/20170122/19904825\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Ffood%2Fart%2F20170122%2F19904825&d=es%2BtSAvE9Ha4YFt1qxhR2QT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=4831b4e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Ffood%2Fart%2F20170122%2F19904825&h=aa4361b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/food/art/20170122/19904825</a><br />\n<br />\n「而是近日因「丸久小山園」而捲起的授權風波。這兩間店同屬和心有限公司代理，我們今日再次向負責人廖傑民查詢，他表明「道頓堀的合約相對清晰，日本那邊亦會於近日發出香港店的開業聲明。」他又補充香港分店是以加盟形式經營，和日本沒有合資關係。我們又追問有關「丸久小山園」的授權問題，他表示已和日本元庵店達成共識，並於不日內發出聲明，暫時不方便解答事件的來龍去脈。我們之後會繼續為大家密切跟進。」<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/supplement/20170124/56217591\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsupplement%2F20170124%2F56217591&d=es%2BtSAvE9Ha4YFt1qxhR2QT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=b2b05cb3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsupplement%2F20170124%2F56217591&h=41e17f92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/supplement/20170124/56217591</a>"}]}